node.contents:
Yiiiiha!! I solved the problem. You were right. The problem was that in my case only the .class and .properties files were compiled. Instead of including some kind of files I excluded the ones I don't want to be compiled. 
<zipfileset src="../lib/poi-ooxml-schemas-3.10-FINAL-20140208.jar" excludes="META-INF/*" /> Thanks for all.
